'''茹魯埃納國家公園'''於2006年宣佈成立，面積約19,000平方公里，是[[巴西|巴西]]第三大國家公園。<ref>[http://wwf.panda.org/what_we_do/where_we_work/amazon/vision_amazon/models/amazon_expeditions/juruena_national_park/factsheets/?74020/Creation-of-a-mega-conservation-corridor-aims-to-reduce-fundamental-conflicts WWF: ''Creation of a (mega) conservation corridor aims to reduce fundamental conflicts'', 26 June 2006] {{Wayback|url=http://wwf.panda.org/what_we_do/where_we_work/amazon/vision_amazon/models/amazon_expeditions/juruena_national_park/factsheets/?74020%2FCreation-of-a-mega-conservation-corridor-aims-to-reduce-fundamental-conflicts |date=20140715001413 }} {{en}}</ref>它位於[[馬托格羅索州|馬托格羅索州]]北部[[茹魯埃納河|茹魯埃納河]]沿岸。

該公園保育多種瀕危物種，如[[美洲豹|美洲豹]]、[[巨獺|巨獺]]及[[角雕|角雕]]等。<ref>[http://www.wwf.de/fileadmin/fm-wwf/pdf_neu/WWF_PB_Juruena.pdf WWF Germany: Nationalpark Juruena] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wwf.de/fileadmin/fm-wwf/pdf_neu/WWF_PB_Juruena.pdf |date=20111009124716 }} ) {{de}}</ref>

